# Risk-Aware Cloud Provisioning Dashboard

This Streamlit application visualizes results from a risk-aware MIP provisioning 
model with 200 Monte Carlo scenarios. It allows users to explore trade-offs 
between cost, capacity risk, and latency SLO violations.

## Features
- Scenario explorer (1â€“200)
- Cost vs. risk trade-off plots
- Instance allocation visualizations
- KPI summaries

## Run Locally
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
